msgid "# Prefill-Decode Disaggregation (Qwen2.5-VL)"
msgstr "# 预填充-解码分离（Qwen2.5-VL）"

msgid "## Getting Started"
msgstr "## 快速开始"

msgid ""
"vLLM-Ascend now supports prefill-decode (PD) disaggregation. This guide "
"provides step-by-step instructions to verify this features in resource-"
"constrained environments."
msgstr "vLLM-Ascend 现已支持预填充-解码（PD）分离。本指南提供在资源受限环境中验证此功能的分步说明。"

msgid ""
"Using the Qwen2.5-VL-7B-Instruct model as an example, use vLLM-Ascend "
"{{vllm_ascend_version}} (with vLLM {{vllm_version}}) on 1 Atlas 800T A2 "
"server to deploy the \"1P1D\" architecture (one Prefiller and one Decoder on"
" the same node). Assume the IP address is 192.0.0.1."
msgstr ""
"以 Qwen2.5-VL-7B-Instruct 模型为例，在 1 台 Atlas 800T A2 服务器上使用 vLLM-Ascend "
"{{vllm_ascend_version}}（搭配 vLLM "
"{{vllm_version}}）部署“1P1D”架构（同一节点上一个预填充器和一个解码器）。假设 IP 地址为 192.0.0.1。"

msgid "## Verify Communication Environment"
msgstr "## 验证通信环境"

msgid "### Verification Process"
msgstr "### 验证流程"

msgid "1. Single Node Verification:"
msgstr "1. 单节点验证："

msgid ""
"Execute the following commands in sequence. The results must all be "
"`success` and the status must be `UP`:"
msgstr "依次执行以下命令。结果必须全部为 `success`，且状态必须为 `UP`："

msgid "2. Check NPU HCCN Configuration:"
msgstr "2. 检查 NPU HCCN 配置："

msgid ""
"Ensure that the hccn.conf file exists in the environment. If using Docker, "
"mount it into the container."
msgstr "确保环境中存在 hccn.conf 文件。如果使用 Docker，请将其挂载到容器中。"

msgid "3. Get NPU IP Addresses"
msgstr "3. 获取 NPU IP 地址"

msgid "4. Cross-Node PING Test"
msgstr "4. 跨节点 PING 测试"

msgid "5. Check NPU TLS Configuration"
msgstr "5. 检查 NPU TLS 配置"

msgid "## Run with Docker"
msgstr "## 使用 Docker 运行"

msgid "Start a Docker container."
msgstr "启动 Docker 容器。"

msgid "## Install Mooncake"
msgstr "## 安装 Mooncake"

msgid ""
"Mooncake is the serving platform for Kimi, a leading LLM service provided by Moonshot AI. Installation and Compilation Guide: <https://github.com/kvcache-ai/Mooncake?tab=readme-ov-file#build-and-use-binaries>.\n"
"First, we need to obtain the Mooncake project. Refer to the following command:"
msgstr ""
"Mooncake 是 Kimi（Moonshot AI 提供的领先 LLM 服务）的服务平台。安装与编译指南：<https://github.com/kvcache-ai/Mooncake?tab=readme-ov-file#build-and-use-binaries>。\n"
"首先，我们需要获取 Mooncake 项目。请参考以下命令："

msgid "(Optional) Replace go install url if the network is poor."
msgstr "（可选）如果网络状况不佳，请替换 go install 的 URL。"

msgid "Install mpi."
msgstr "安装 mpi。"

msgid ""
"Install the relevant dependencies. The installation of Go is not required."
msgstr "安装相关依赖。无需安装 Go。"

msgid "Compile and install."
msgstr "编译并安装。"

msgid "Set environment variables."
msgstr "设置环境变量。"

msgid "**Note:**"
msgstr "**注意：**"

msgid ""
"- Adjust the Python path according to your specific Python installation\n"
"- Ensure `/usr/local/lib` and `/usr/local/lib64` are in your `LD_LIBRARY_PATH`"
msgstr ""
"- 根据您的具体 Python 安装调整 Python 路径\n"
"- 确保 `/usr/local/lib` 和 `/usr/local/lib64` 位于您的 `LD_LIBRARY_PATH` 中"

msgid "## Prefiller/Decoder Deployment"
msgstr "## 预填充器/解码器部署"

msgid ""
"We can run the following scripts to launch a server on the prefiller/decoder"
" NPU, respectively."
msgstr "我们可以运行以下脚本，分别在预填充器/解码器 NPU 上启动服务器。"

msgid "=== \"Prefiller\""
msgstr "=== \"预填充器\""

msgid "=== \"Decoder\""
msgstr "=== \"解码器\""

msgid ""
"If you want to run \"2P1D\", please set ASCEND_RT_VISIBLE_DEVICES and port "
"to different values for each P process."
msgstr "如果要运行“2P1D”，请为每个 P 进程设置不同的 ASCEND_RT_VISIBLE_DEVICES 和端口值。"

msgid "## Example Proxy for Deployment"
msgstr "## 部署示例代理"

msgid ""
"Run a proxy server on the same node with the prefiller service instance. You"
" can get the proxy program in the repository's examples: "
"[load\\_balance\\_proxy\\_server\\_example.py](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/main/examples/disaggregated_prefill_v1/load_balance_proxy_server_example.py)"
msgstr ""
"在与预填充器服务实例相同的节点上运行代理服务器。您可以在仓库的示例中获取代理程序：[load\\_balance\\_proxy\\_server\\_example.py](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/main/examples/disaggregated_prefill_v1/load_balance_proxy_server_example.py)"

msgid "## Verification"
msgstr "## 验证"

msgid "Check service health using the proxy server endpoint."
msgstr "使用代理服务器端点检查服务健康状态。"

msgid "|Parameter  | Meaning |"
msgstr "|参数 | 含义 |"

msgid "| --port | Port of proxy |"
msgstr "| --port | 代理端口 |"

msgid "| --prefiller-port | All ports of prefill |"
msgstr "| --prefiller-port | 预填充的所有端口 |"

msgid "| --decoder-ports | All ports of decoder |"
msgstr "| --decoder-ports | 解码器的所有端口 |"
